item.title: Dear Petavera
item.dc:creator: vlad
item.content:encoded:
Non-wordpress PSD -> HTML example

  This page is made from a demo PSD file. The code and PSD file can be found on Github.   Live Site Code on Git Hub  

Wordpress PSD -> HTML Example

This WordPress example utilizies the Activello theme as its base and added a custom page and css. The PSD is just a sample PSD file and not one used on an actual live site. The wp-content folder and post data can be found on git hub. The original PSD file can be found in the wp-content/images folder. Please note: The original PSD file calles for Helvetica Neuva font , which I currently do not own. I used the Roboto font instead. If this was an actual project, the Helvetica Neuva font can be easily installed in the function.php and css files. Live Site Code on Git Hub
